-- Indonesia’s Pertamina Seeks Low-Sulfur Crude for June Delivery
-- B y   R a m s e y   A l - R i k a b i
-- 2012-04-05T01:55:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-05/indonesia-s-pertamina-seeks-low-sulfur-crude-for-june-delivery.html
Indonesia ’s  PT Pertamina (PERT)  is seeking
low-sulfur crude for delivery in June, according to a document
obtained by Bloomberg News.  The state-owned company has tendered to buy cargoes of
either 600,000 barrels or 950,000 barrels to be delivered to
either its Cilacap or Balikpapan refineries.  Details of the tender are as follows:  To contact the reporter on this story:
